HARNAM SINGH, Also Known as Pritam Singh, v. I. F. WIXON, District Director of Immigration and Naturalization for the Port of San Francisco. No. 9768. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. April 23, 1941. Joseph P. Fallon, of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. Frank J. Hennessy, U. S. Atty., of San Francisco, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal herein dismissed, that a decree be filed and entered accordingly, and that mandate of this court in this cause issue forthwith.
